	<h1 class="title">后摇乐队惘闻新专辑《岁月鸿沟》就要来了，还有巡演</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/429696/small/429696.jpg?1453172978" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">杨京楷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-15 07:10:31 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25491/medium/25491.jpg?1460639674" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="25491" data-title="《后摇乐队惘闻新专辑《岁月鸿沟》就要来了，还有巡演》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25491/medium/25491.jpg?1460639674" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/25491.html?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
